ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: The identifier of the population group as defined in the measure definition.

ivardefs.name: measureScore
ivardefs.desc: The measure score for this population group, calculated as appropriate for the measure type and scoring method, and based on the contents of the populations defined in the group.

ivardefs.name: population_
ivardefs.desc: The populations that make up the population group, one for each type of population appropriate for the measure.

ivardefs.name: stratifier_
ivardefs.desc: When a measure includes multiple stratifiers, there will be a stratifier group for each stratifier defined by the measure.

properties.desc: The results of the calculation, one for each population group in the measure.
